<reference id="callback_imediarecorderobserver_onrecorderinfoupdated">
    <title><ph keyref="onRecorderInfoUpdated" /></title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc">录制信息更新回调。</ph></shortdesc>
    <prolog>
        <metadata>
            <keywords>
                <indexterm keyref="onRecorderInfoUpdated" />
            </keywords>
        </metadata>
    </prolog>
    <refbody>
        <section id="prototype">
            <p outputclass="codeblock">
            <codeblock props="android" outputclass="language-java">void onRecorderInfoUpdated(RecorderInfo info);</codeblock>
            <codeblock props="ios mac" outputclass="language-objectivec">- (void)mediaRecorder:(AgoraMediaRecorder* _Nonnull)recorder informationDidUpdated:(AgoraMediaRecorderInfo* _Nonnull)info;</codeblock>
            <codeblock props="cpp" outputclass="language-cpp">virtual void onRecorderInfoUpdated(const RecorderInfo&amp; info){};</codeblock>
            <codeblock props="electron" outputclass="language-typescript">  onRecorderInfoUpdated?(info: RecorderInfo): void;</codeblock>
            <codeblock props="unity" outputclass="language-csharp">public virtual void OnRecorderInfoUpdated(RecorderInfo info) {}</codeblock>
            <codeblock props="rn" outputclass="language-typescript">  onRecorderInfoUpdated?(info: RecorderInfo): void;</codeblock>
            <codeblock props="flutter" outputclass="language-dart">final void Function(RecorderInfo info)? onRecorderInfoUpdated;</codeblock> </p>
        </section>
        <section id="detailed_desc">
            <p>成功注册该回调并开启本地音视频流录制后，SDK 会根据你在 <xref keyref="MediaRecorderConfiguration" /> 中设置的 <parmname>recorderInfoUpdateInterval</parmname> 的值周期性触发该回调，报告当前录制文件的文件名、时长和大小。</p>
        </section>
        <section id="parameters">
            <title><ph keyref="callback-section-title" /></title>
            
            <parml>
            <plentry>
                <pt>info</pt>
                <pd>录制文件信息。详见 <xref keyref="RecorderInfo" />。</pd>
            </plentry>
                <plentry props="apple">
                    <pt>recorder</pt>
                    <pd><xref keyref="IMediaRecorder" /> 对象。</pd>
                </plentry>
            </parml> </section>
    </refbody>
</reference>